          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Fire Sale Loophole Closing Act</b></p> <p>This bill restricts the transfer of business inventory firearms by a firearms importer, manufacturer, or dealer whose licensed is revoked or denied. </p> <p>A violator is subject to criminal penalties&#8212;a fine, prison term of up to one year, or both. </p>]]></text>
